TI  - A smart contract and IPFS-based framework for secure electric vehicles at station
T2  - SUSTAINABLE ENERGY GRIDS & NETWORKS
LA  - English
KW  - Electric vehicles
KW  - Charging stations
KW  - Charging synchronization
