TI  - Electric Mobility Transition, Intelligent Digital Platforms, and Grid-Vehicle Integration Models: A Systematic Review
T2  - WORLD ELECTRIC VEHICLE JOURNAL
LA  - English
KW  - electric mobility transition
KW  - intelligent digital platforms
KW  - grid-vehicle integration
KW  - Industry 4.0 technologies
KW  - smart charging infrastructure
KW  - vehicle-to-grid (V2G)
